WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.344 --> 01:37.712
=Episode 40=

01:38.160 --> 01:38.959
General Wang.

01:39.959 --> 01:41.399
Do you want to go dance too?

01:45.839 --> 01:47.280
Go dance!

01:47.984 --> 01:48.560
Let's go.

01:48.560 --> 01:49.720
- Dance!
- Dance!

02:02.759 --> 02:04.679
- Good!
- Good!

02:06.928 --> 02:10.934
♪My life is full of ups and downs♪

02:13.104 --> 02:17.264
♪Every wound shows traces of love♪

02:18.192 --> 02:23.457
♪I've seen all the withering plants
in this world♪

02:23.902 --> 02:27.120
♪Until you went over the hills♪

02:27.376 --> 02:29.843
♪To come close to me♪

02:31.639 --> 02:32.560
You're back.

02:36.000 --> 02:36.840
Are you cold?

02:37.680 --> 02:41.745
♪Quietly full of joy and sorrow♪

02:42.320 --> 02:48.528
♪When it's over, I stand in the light♪

02:51.079 --> 02:52.840
Suixue Pass is nothing like the capital.

02:53.720 --> 02:54.560
Even in this season,

02:55.599 --> 02:56.799
it's still chilly at night.

02:57.582 --> 03:00.066
♪Send love far away♪

03:00.848 --> 03:02.928
♪As I travel through wind and frost♪

03:03.599 --> 03:04.960
Had a bad time in the capital?

03:05.720 --> 03:06.928
Why didn't you tell me before?

03:06.928 --> 03:12.144
♪You never forget me,
and I always miss you♪

03:14.680 --> 03:16.560
You only tell the good news,
not the bad.

03:19.919 --> 03:22.160
You are so nagging.

03:22.400 --> 03:23.960
I haven't even started nagging yet.

03:24.240 --> 03:25.400
Let me ask you,

03:25.639 --> 03:27.319
how did you come all the way here?

03:27.880 --> 03:29.039
How many days did it take?

03:29.599 --> 03:31.479
Did you come with a caravan,
or by post-horse?

03:32.039 --> 03:32.880
And,

03:33.799 --> 03:35.720
were you traveling alone the whole time?

03:35.720 --> 03:37.039
Don't you know it's dangerous?

03:39.120 --> 03:40.560
I came all the way here to you,

03:41.240 --> 03:42.840
yet you're just asking me questions.

03:44.496 --> 03:49.392
♪In every dawn and dusk, life endures♪

03:53.160 --> 03:55.000
If you reach that forest up ahead first,

03:55.359 --> 03:56.759
I'll allow you to drink tonight.

03:57.200 --> 03:58.032
- Hyah.
- Hyah.

03:58.880 --> 03:59.880
You're cheating!

04:00.079 --> 04:01.039
Mo Xiuyao.

04:01.039 --> 04:01.840
Have you no shame?

04:04.000 --> 04:05.120
Lieyun, hurry!

04:06.120 --> 04:07.440
It fears to win too easily,

04:07.840 --> 04:09.319
and someone would ignore me at night.

04:11.792 --> 04:17.705
♪We return to where time began♪

04:19.008 --> 04:24.656
♪You say,
there's still a long way ahead♪

04:26.440 --> 04:27.536
We have three joyous things

04:27.719 --> 04:29.199
to celebrate in today's feast.

04:29.440 --> 04:30.680
The first joy,

04:30.880 --> 04:31.880
congratulate His Highness

04:31.880 --> 04:33.959
on his triumphant return
from Suixue Pass.

04:41.399 --> 04:42.719
The second joy,

04:44.159 --> 04:45.232
congratulate Mr. Gu

04:45.399 --> 04:47.399
on his promotion to Jingzhao Prefect.

04:48.240 --> 04:49.040
Mr. Gu,

04:49.040 --> 04:50.360
since we are both in the capital,

04:50.360 --> 04:53.240
please come to my shop more often.

04:53.240 --> 04:54.560
Of course.

04:54.560 --> 04:56.719
I will do my best.

04:56.719 --> 04:57.480
Prefect Gu,

04:57.480 --> 04:59.472
please look after us.

04:59.472 --> 05:00.519
Of course.

05:00.784 --> 05:01.440
Come on.

05:03.759 --> 05:04.800
The third joy,

05:06.279 --> 05:08.208
congratulate Zhuang
on moving to a new home.

05:08.600 --> 05:10.199
May your new mansion

05:10.199 --> 05:11.279
bring lasting blessings.

05:11.560 --> 05:12.600
Thank you, everyone.

05:14.360 --> 05:15.600
Let me add one more thing.

05:15.680 --> 05:16.880
The capital had a turmoil,

05:17.079 --> 05:18.079
with drastic changes.

05:18.240 --> 05:19.880
We have survived this calamity safely,

05:20.839 --> 05:22.319
which is the greatest blessing.

05:22.600 --> 05:24.120
So, let's raise this cup of peace

05:24.560 --> 05:25.880
to the rest of our lives,

05:26.480 --> 05:27.888
filled with happiness.

05:28.680 --> 05:29.519
Come on.

05:36.040 --> 05:36.880
By the way, Feibai,

05:37.279 --> 05:38.519
when did you get back?

05:39.600 --> 05:40.519
A couple of days ago.

05:41.000 --> 05:43.319
I returned in a hurry
and didn't have time to tell you.

05:44.120 --> 05:45.680
Feibai, pass me the wine.

05:49.440 --> 05:50.880
Ran out of wine. I'll go get some.

05:51.519 --> 05:52.159
Someone!

05:52.159 --> 05:53.759
No need. I'll go get it myself.

05:56.759 --> 05:57.719
Be careful.

06:04.519 --> 06:05.319
Feibai.

06:07.319 --> 06:08.639
What's wrong?

06:08.639 --> 06:09.399
It's nothing.

06:09.399 --> 06:11.399
I probably just drank too fast.

06:13.639 --> 06:15.759
What's your plan next?

06:16.880 --> 06:17.880
No plans.

06:18.319 --> 06:20.240
I'll just wander around.

06:20.800 --> 06:22.959
I'll stop for some days
if I see beautiful scenery.

06:23.120 --> 06:23.920
If I get fine wine,

06:24.040 --> 06:25.199
I'll just get dead drunk.

06:25.319 --> 06:26.480
You're leaving?

06:27.759 --> 06:29.079
What about Lady Yusheng?

06:30.639 --> 06:31.519
She and I

06:31.680 --> 06:33.159
just encountered by chance.

06:33.639 --> 06:34.920
Accompanying for a while

06:35.360 --> 06:36.480
is already a blessing.

06:36.959 --> 06:37.959
From now on,

06:38.079 --> 06:39.519
she'll pursue her splendid future,

06:39.880 --> 06:41.639
and I'll go travel around.

06:42.199 --> 06:43.399
Since our paths are different,

06:43.959 --> 06:45.120
no need to force each other.

06:47.560 --> 06:48.560
But didn't you

06:48.560 --> 06:50.480
just buy a mansion in the capital?

06:51.079 --> 06:52.440
Why are you leaving?

06:52.959 --> 06:54.000
All feasts

06:54.159 --> 06:55.240
must come to an end.

06:56.040 --> 06:57.880
Besides, the whole Lishan thing is over.

06:57.880 --> 06:59.440
And I am a free spirit.

06:59.639 --> 07:01.199
If I stay in one place too long,

07:01.480 --> 07:02.800
my bones get soft.

07:03.000 --> 07:03.920
Li.

07:03.920 --> 07:05.680
Let me go for a free life.

07:07.719 --> 07:08.920
After you leave,

07:09.319 --> 07:10.600
will you come back?

07:14.079 --> 07:14.920
Hard to say.

07:16.880 --> 07:18.079
I might settle down

07:19.319 --> 07:20.360
in any place.

07:28.560 --> 07:29.120
Wine's here.

07:29.440 --> 07:30.079
Let's go in.

07:33.759 --> 07:36.159
I know all this by heart already.

07:37.360 --> 07:40.000
What's the secret between you two?
Why did you two go out to talk?

07:41.399 --> 07:42.480
I told Li

07:43.159 --> 07:44.360
that I'll take a long journey,

07:44.759 --> 07:45.480
traveling around

07:45.880 --> 07:46.839
and living a free life.

07:47.800 --> 07:49.199
Traveling around

07:49.480 --> 07:50.319
is wonderful!

07:50.319 --> 07:51.440
Yes, it's wonderful.

07:51.519 --> 07:52.360
Feibai,

07:52.600 --> 07:53.560
although we

07:53.680 --> 07:55.399
met rather late,

07:55.399 --> 07:56.680
I admire your

07:56.680 --> 07:57.839
carefree spirit.

07:58.040 --> 07:58.839
Don't worry.

07:59.279 --> 08:01.680
My Feng family's businesses
are all over the land.

08:01.680 --> 08:02.959
Wherever you go,

08:03.079 --> 08:04.279
as long as you give your name,

08:04.959 --> 08:05.959
you have a place to stay,

08:05.959 --> 08:06.960
wine and meat for free.

08:08.159 --> 08:09.600
Wait, wait.

08:11.480 --> 08:13.959
Mr. Li, with your chivalrous heart

08:14.159 --> 08:15.319
and great martial skills,

08:15.319 --> 08:16.519
in the martial world,

08:16.519 --> 08:18.800
you will surely make
a great name for yourself.

08:19.399 --> 08:22.199
I won't wish you
greater martial arts then.

08:22.360 --> 08:23.360
When you're out,

08:23.600 --> 08:24.680
safety is the best thing.

08:24.920 --> 08:25.719
To you.

08:26.120 --> 08:26.920
Cheers!

08:26.959 --> 08:27.600
Thank you both.

08:27.880 --> 08:28.680
Mr. Li,

08:29.399 --> 08:31.800
we really bonded through our fight.

08:32.360 --> 08:33.279
I'm from Bashu,

08:33.279 --> 08:35.200
so let me send you off
with a Bashu saying.

08:37.080 --> 08:39.159
Bro, listen to me.

08:39.600 --> 08:40.759
Stand tall,

08:40.960 --> 08:42.200
and keep your word.

08:42.480 --> 08:43.480
Go make your mark,

08:44.799 --> 08:46.320
and don't be a fool.

08:47.120 --> 08:48.960
I don't understand a single word.

08:51.600 --> 08:52.360
Come on.

08:53.600 --> 08:54.720
Let him drink less.

08:55.880 --> 08:56.679
Feibai,

08:58.480 --> 08:59.360
safe travels.

09:03.360 --> 09:04.480
Wherever you go,

09:04.720 --> 09:05.960
remember to write to me.

09:06.679 --> 09:07.399
I know.

09:07.399 --> 09:08.200
Don't worry.

09:09.559 --> 09:10.439
Take good care of Li.

09:11.639 --> 09:12.320
I will.

09:13.639 --> 09:14.439
Feibai.

09:19.559 --> 09:21.639
Don't lament that life is fleeting
like morning dew,

09:22.200 --> 09:24.240
don't complain
that the road ahead is long.

09:25.039 --> 09:27.639
Old friends will always reunite,

09:28.519 --> 09:31.559
if not in the green hills,
then in the wine land.

09:32.200 --> 09:33.000
Good!

09:33.720 --> 09:35.240
Old friends will always reunite,

09:35.639 --> 09:37.919
if not in the green hills,
then in the wine land.

09:37.919 --> 09:38.720
Good poem!

09:39.480 --> 09:40.159
Cheers!

09:52.880 --> 09:54.240
Then I'll take my leave first.

09:54.559 --> 09:55.639
Farewell.

09:56.559 --> 09:58.039
What a heavy rain.

10:00.480 --> 10:02.000
When will you depart tomorrow?

10:02.000 --> 10:02.960
I'll see you off.

10:03.360 --> 10:04.159
No need.

10:04.639 --> 10:05.720
Though oceans apart,

10:06.399 --> 10:07.279
fate reunites us.

10:10.799 --> 10:11.559
Take care.

10:16.200 --> 10:17.480
You fall asleep standing up?

10:18.080 --> 10:18.672
Come on.

10:19.000 --> 10:19.880
I'll sober you up.

10:52.399 --> 10:53.080
Feibai.

10:54.919 --> 10:55.720
You're back.

10:56.240 --> 10:57.480
Why have you been out so long?

11:06.480 --> 11:07.360
What's this?

11:09.080 --> 11:09.919
Don't recognize it?

11:10.080 --> 11:10.880
Money.

11:15.120 --> 11:16.399
What do you mean?

11:16.720 --> 11:17.639
Nothing.

11:18.320 --> 11:19.320
I'm leaving.

11:19.320 --> 11:20.320
I'll leave the capital.

11:20.720 --> 11:21.919
Keep the money.

11:22.279 --> 11:23.960
If you want to leave Xiangqi Pavilion,

11:24.080 --> 11:25.200
use it to buy your freedom.

11:25.200 --> 11:26.159
If not,

11:26.600 --> 11:27.919
just keep it

11:28.159 --> 11:29.840
as a token of our acquaintance.

11:31.919 --> 11:33.240
I'm famous in the capital.

11:33.279 --> 11:35.184
Those nobles spend lavishly

11:35.184 --> 11:36.720
just to win a smile from me.

11:37.120 --> 11:38.439
Do I need this paltry sum?

11:40.600 --> 11:41.399
Li Feibai.

11:41.960 --> 11:43.360
We've known each other for years.

11:43.600 --> 11:44.559
If you're leaving,

11:44.880 --> 11:46.960
at least tell me in advance.

11:47.439 --> 11:48.880
What do you mean now?

11:49.439 --> 11:50.960
Why are you so angry?

11:51.320 --> 11:52.480
Am I angry?

11:52.679 --> 11:53.840
I'm not angry.

11:54.679 --> 11:56.439
Then what are you doing right now?

11:57.080 --> 11:58.960
I'm just reasoning with you.

12:02.759 --> 12:03.639
I see now.

12:04.080 --> 12:06.080
You can't bear to see me leave

12:06.080 --> 12:07.600
and want to come with me?

12:08.600 --> 12:09.799
Don't be ridiculous.

12:10.880 --> 12:12.200
I'm a man roaming around.

12:12.679 --> 12:14.880
I sleep rough and live by the sword.

12:15.080 --> 12:16.639
My tomorrow may not come.

12:16.919 --> 12:18.256
When I'm in a good mood,

12:18.256 --> 12:20.000
I might play along and sweet-talk you,

12:20.000 --> 12:21.439
spending lavishly on you.

12:21.679 --> 12:22.640
When I'm not on my luck,

12:22.640 --> 12:24.400
I can't even afford a hot meal,

12:24.400 --> 12:26.320
not to mention to look after you.

12:27.480 --> 12:30.080
I remember you said before
that you can't leave the capital,

12:30.320 --> 12:31.840
and you had enough of hard time,

12:31.840 --> 12:33.120
so you can't suffer now.

12:33.439 --> 12:34.880
You said all that, right?

12:35.039 --> 12:36.240
- I...
- Enough!

12:38.519 --> 12:39.320
Yusheng,

12:41.919 --> 12:42.679
as a top courtesan

12:42.679 --> 12:45.080
in the world of pleasure for many years,

12:45.320 --> 12:47.120
you should understand better than me

12:47.320 --> 12:49.439
what it means to let things go.

12:51.679 --> 12:52.519
You scum!

14:01.679 --> 14:02.480
Run!

14:41.000 --> 14:41.799
Let's have a game.

14:46.200 --> 14:47.000
What's wrong?

14:47.360 --> 14:48.840
You don't look very happy.

14:51.240 --> 14:52.919
I'll take you to Qingfeng Mingyue Tower.

14:53.439 --> 14:54.399
Feng Zhiyao said

14:54.439 --> 14:56.279
there's a new chef there,

14:56.439 --> 14:58.000
and he's excellent at Lingnan cuisine.

15:01.320 --> 15:02.120
How about

15:02.519 --> 15:03.600
a walk in the suburbs?

15:06.399 --> 15:06.960
Well,

15:07.279 --> 15:10.039
I'll have Qingyu set up
a small table in the pavilion.

15:10.360 --> 15:11.720
Let's drink some warm wine.

15:13.120 --> 15:13.960
Forget it.

15:15.480 --> 15:16.600
You even reject wine?

15:24.720 --> 15:26.000
It seems you are

15:26.840 --> 15:28.240
truly upset.

15:33.639 --> 15:34.960
Actually, I've never known

15:35.480 --> 15:37.039
how good your swordsmanship really is.

15:37.759 --> 15:38.840
Compared to mine,

15:39.360 --> 15:40.000
how is it?

15:42.519 --> 15:44.080
Naturally, mine is better.

15:44.639 --> 15:46.200
I am Master Zhu's disciple, after all.

15:49.039 --> 15:49.840
True.

15:50.360 --> 15:52.880
They all say Master Zhu
is the Sword Immortal of our time,

15:53.120 --> 15:55.279
who created the Milky Way Technique

15:55.279 --> 15:56.600
and the Forty-Six Form Technique.

15:57.720 --> 15:58.759
But people also say

15:59.759 --> 16:02.360
a good chef might not be a good teacher.

16:02.759 --> 16:04.439
He has excellent swordsmanship,

16:04.559 --> 16:06.159
but he might not be able

16:06.639 --> 16:07.960
to make great disciples.

16:09.159 --> 16:10.159
What do you mean?

16:12.159 --> 16:13.039
Let's have a contest.

16:17.880 --> 16:18.679
Tell me,

16:18.799 --> 16:19.439
how to compete?

16:19.639 --> 16:20.639
Blades are blind.

16:20.919 --> 16:22.512
I fear I may hurt you accidentally.

16:24.519 --> 16:25.679
Why not use branches instead?

16:27.000 --> 16:28.399
Whoever's blossoms fall off first

16:28.399 --> 16:29.399
loses.

16:32.600 --> 16:33.759
Then be careful.

17:03.519 --> 17:04.199
You lost.

17:05.800 --> 17:07.360
I'd love to lose to you for a lifetime.

17:09.560 --> 17:10.360
Your Highness.

17:10.360 --> 17:11.159
Your Highness.

17:12.800 --> 17:13.679
Your Highnesses.

17:14.360 --> 17:15.320
News from the palace.

17:15.320 --> 17:17.439
Her Majesty is very ill.
She summoned Her Highness.

17:27.880 --> 17:28.479
Your Majesty.

17:28.760 --> 17:29.968
Princess Ding has arrived.

17:32.999 --> 17:33.679
Your Majesty.

17:33.679 --> 17:36.120
You've been sitting too long.
You should lie down and rest.

17:38.239 --> 17:39.280
You may leave.

17:41.479 --> 17:42.280
Your Majesty.

17:44.120 --> 17:44.959
Leave.

17:50.159 --> 17:50.999
All of you, leave.

18:01.239 --> 18:02.080
Come up and sit.

18:12.840 --> 18:14.239
I asked you to come

18:15.639 --> 18:16.639
because I thought

18:17.479 --> 18:20.040
you have something to say to me.

18:22.560 --> 18:24.679
I have nothing to say to you.

18:27.399 --> 18:29.080
I owe your mother.

18:30.639 --> 18:32.520
Don't you want to seek justice for her?

18:33.159 --> 18:34.399
Before I left the mountain,

18:35.280 --> 18:37.159
I had four people in mind
I wanted to eliminate.

18:38.439 --> 18:39.840
And you were indeed one of them.

18:43.919 --> 18:45.159
What number am I?

18:46.999 --> 18:47.800
Fourth.

18:49.880 --> 18:50.999
The last one.

18:52.600 --> 18:53.639
Why?

18:54.399 --> 18:56.144
Your Majesty holds
high status and power,

18:56.199 --> 18:57.199
difficult to deal with.

18:59.159 --> 19:00.040
Then now

19:00.959 --> 19:02.280
is a perfect opportunity.

19:04.479 --> 19:05.280
Actually,

19:05.880 --> 19:07.479
my every day staying in Anqing Palace

19:08.040 --> 19:09.040
was an opportunity.

19:10.999 --> 19:12.639
Then why didn't you kill me?

19:14.639 --> 19:15.679
Within the palace walls,

19:16.360 --> 19:17.199
if I killed you,

19:17.399 --> 19:18.600
I couldn't have escaped.

19:19.040 --> 19:19.880
It wasn't worth it.

19:29.199 --> 19:30.439
Was it not worth it,

19:31.800 --> 19:33.040
or do you think

19:35.239 --> 19:36.600
I am different from them?

19:39.719 --> 19:40.840
Who are you referring to?

19:41.600 --> 19:42.760
Since I took power,

19:43.719 --> 19:45.080
I have always issued new reforms.

19:46.120 --> 19:47.360
I reformed the waterway,

19:49.159 --> 19:51.040
reduced thirty-thousand
trackers conscripted,

19:51.320 --> 19:54.040
cut taxes by forty percent,

19:54.959 --> 19:56.239
established women's schools,

19:57.239 --> 19:58.352
female-led households,

19:59.040 --> 20:00.320
and Women's Chamber of Commerce.

20:00.959 --> 20:01.719
Look,

20:02.840 --> 20:04.159
today's Dachu,

20:05.679 --> 20:07.479
the Grand Canal
connects north and south,

20:08.479 --> 20:09.760
the granaries are full,

20:10.320 --> 20:11.560
rites and morals thrive,

20:12.159 --> 20:14.919
women's schools are established
across prefectures and counties,

20:15.880 --> 20:18.560
and even those from humble origins
can ascend to the court.

20:18.919 --> 20:20.080
With such accomplishments,

20:21.439 --> 20:22.928
how do I compare to the late emperor?

20:28.560 --> 20:29.360
You tell me.

20:30.479 --> 20:31.679
How do I compare

20:33.600 --> 20:34.399
to the late emperor?

20:39.760 --> 20:41.679
Grandfather once talked
about Your Majesty.

20:42.959 --> 20:44.080
Would you like to hear it?

20:45.439 --> 20:46.479
What did he say?

20:46.919 --> 20:47.880
Ms. Guo

20:48.919 --> 20:49.840
has talent and ability,

20:50.280 --> 20:51.439
but lacks benevolence.

20:51.880 --> 20:53.360
She can hold the supreme power,

20:53.880 --> 20:55.520
but can't bear the people's suffering.

20:56.959 --> 20:57.719
He

20:59.120 --> 21:00.560
said that about me?

21:02.880 --> 21:03.760
Pedantic!

21:06.360 --> 21:07.840
Truly pedantic!

21:08.320 --> 21:09.600
It's simply because

21:10.840 --> 21:13.199
I rule as a woman.

21:14.040 --> 21:14.840
Since ancient times,

21:15.280 --> 21:16.360
every transition of power

21:17.320 --> 21:18.320
has been

21:19.159 --> 21:21.080
stained with blood on the palace steps.

21:22.360 --> 21:23.520
If I don't kill,

21:24.159 --> 21:25.360
I will be killed.

21:25.880 --> 21:27.239
I was forced by the circumstances.

21:28.280 --> 21:29.679
Only by first protecting myself

21:30.320 --> 21:32.040
can I then practice benevolence.

21:32.639 --> 21:33.439
It's a pity

21:34.600 --> 21:35.800
that a great scholar like him

21:37.199 --> 21:38.560
couldn't understand

21:39.399 --> 21:40.679
such a principle.

21:43.959 --> 21:45.080
When I left the mountain,

21:45.560 --> 21:46.880
I once passed through Longqu,

21:47.959 --> 21:50.512
and saw the prefecture building
an official road to the capital.

21:51.560 --> 21:54.520
The officials all praised Your Majesty's
benevolence and achievements,

21:54.639 --> 21:56.360
but the common people
were all cursing you.

21:56.959 --> 21:58.159
Do you know why?

22:01.159 --> 22:02.959
Fastest route was required
to build the road.

22:03.280 --> 22:04.656
Yet the people refused to leave,

22:04.880 --> 22:07.239
so the officials destroyed the fields
and cut off the paths,

22:07.239 --> 22:08.840
forcing them to abandon fields
and leave.

22:08.840 --> 22:10.439
This is your so-called benevolence.

22:13.760 --> 22:15.760
The mountain roads
in Longzhou are hard to access.

22:17.760 --> 22:18.760
Building an official road

22:19.919 --> 22:21.760
benefits the nation and the people.

22:22.360 --> 22:24.120
They failed to see the bigger picture.

22:25.120 --> 22:26.560
You studied at Lishan Mountain.

22:27.360 --> 22:29.040
You know the methods
of road construction.

22:29.560 --> 22:30.360
Taking a detour,

22:30.679 --> 22:31.479
building a bridge,

22:31.479 --> 22:33.080
and rerouting the road for fields.

22:33.080 --> 22:34.959
Proceed in due order
and attend to all aspects.

22:34.959 --> 22:36.880
But you chose the fastest,

22:37.439 --> 22:39.399
yet cruelest method.

22:39.679 --> 22:41.040
You can't please everyone.

22:42.560 --> 22:44.360
Someone has to make sacrifice.

22:48.919 --> 22:50.120
Sacrificing farmers' fields

22:50.880 --> 22:52.400
to improve the capital's transport.

22:53.120 --> 22:54.280
Just like back then,

22:54.999 --> 22:56.280
sacrificing the Heiyun Cavalry

22:56.919 --> 22:58.679
to secure your control over the court.

22:59.439 --> 23:01.072
Eliminating the Eastern Palace's heir

23:01.399 --> 23:03.080
to help you ascend to the throne.

23:03.399 --> 23:04.840
The prosperous era you seek

23:05.479 --> 23:07.199
is just the deep-rooted obsession of you

23:07.520 --> 23:09.840
who cannot ascend the throne.

23:09.999 --> 23:11.520
The eternal legacy you mention

23:11.760 --> 23:13.919
is just an excuse
to fill the fear in your heart.

23:13.919 --> 23:15.120
To prove to the throne,

23:15.159 --> 23:15.959
to the court,

23:15.959 --> 23:17.280
and to the world

23:17.479 --> 23:18.760
that you were capable enough

23:19.360 --> 23:21.159
to get and secure the throne.

23:22.040 --> 23:23.239
In that case,

23:26.439 --> 23:27.639
why didn't you kill me?

23:33.600 --> 23:35.239
Whether Your Majesty is guilty,

23:36.199 --> 23:37.999
the law will deliver a fair judgment.

23:52.600 --> 23:53.399
Your Majesty.

23:53.639 --> 23:54.840
What's wrong, Your Majesty?

23:55.679 --> 23:56.479
Imperial physician.

23:56.479 --> 23:57.360
Imperial physician!

23:57.479 --> 23:58.560
Get the imperial physician!

23:59.600 --> 24:01.919
Her Majesty's pulse
at cun, guan, and chi positions

24:01.919 --> 24:03.159
is faint.

24:03.280 --> 24:04.479
Her heart energy is declining.

24:04.560 --> 24:05.760
Her pectoral qi is sinking.

24:05.800 --> 24:07.639
It's caused by an excess
of the five emotions.

24:07.919 --> 24:09.639
Prolonged anxiety damaged the spleen,

24:09.959 --> 24:12.120
and combined with overexertion,

24:12.360 --> 24:14.719
it has led to deficiency
in both heart and spleen.

24:14.919 --> 24:16.159
Both qi and blood depleted.

24:16.320 --> 24:18.479
Even if Qibo

24:18.479 --> 24:19.719
and Bian Que were still here,

24:19.719 --> 24:21.520
they had no way to cure her either.

24:36.280 --> 24:37.552
(As an emperor,)

24:37.959 --> 24:39.679
(I believe you're guilty
to all the people.)

24:40.439 --> 24:41.679
(I represent the law.)

24:42.040 --> 24:45.360
(The people and those aggrieved souls)

24:45.639 --> 24:46.880
(cannot forgive you.)

24:54.999 --> 24:56.159
(But as a son,)

24:56.840 --> 24:57.880
(I still remember)

24:58.520 --> 24:59.239
(it was you)

24:59.760 --> 25:01.840
(who personally taught me
to write my first word.)

25:02.840 --> 25:03.520
(It was you)

25:03.959 --> 25:06.120
(who kept vigil by my sickbed
night after night.)

25:06.840 --> 25:08.600
(It was you who helped me ascend)

25:08.679 --> 25:10.639
(to the imperial throne
under immense pressure.)

25:11.639 --> 25:13.080
(You fed me with your milk,)

25:13.399 --> 25:14.880
(and raised me with your efforts.)

25:15.760 --> 25:17.719
(You will always be my mother.)

25:23.360 --> 25:24.320
(The books say,)

25:24.999 --> 25:26.399
(life is but a passing inn.)

25:27.159 --> 25:28.399
(Even with wide roads,)

25:29.080 --> 25:30.800
(in the end, each walks their own way,)

25:31.399 --> 25:32.679
(enduring one's own trials.)

25:42.880 --> 25:44.479
(Some are trapped by love and desire,)

25:45.600 --> 25:47.880
(drowning in the bitter sea
of unattainable longing.)

25:53.199 --> 25:54.520
(Some adhere to the Dao,)

25:55.560 --> 25:58.608
(walking alone
through the endless long night.)

26:04.199 --> 26:05.479
(Some enjoy solitude,)

26:05.719 --> 26:08.752
(savoring loneliness
in boundless silence.)

26:17.679 --> 26:18.959
(Some hide in the shadows,)

26:20.399 --> 26:23.880
(wandering and searching
amidst a crumbling fate.)

26:34.840 --> 26:37.479
(But the miracle of life
lies precisely in this.)

26:39.040 --> 26:40.999
(It is like a flickering lamp,)

26:41.840 --> 26:43.040
(torn between light and dark.)

26:44.479 --> 26:45.880
(You can never tell)

26:46.159 --> 26:48.679
(what kind of light or darkness)

26:49.399 --> 26:51.040
(you will encounter.)

26:53.199 --> 26:54.439
(But what matters is)

26:55.800 --> 26:56.800
(that you)

26:57.399 --> 26:59.360
(must always move forward.)

27:10.120 --> 27:10.800
Prefect.

27:14.959 --> 27:16.520
This is a gift from the people.

27:16.800 --> 27:18.080
Hope you will accept it.

27:26.480 --> 27:33.744
(Upright and Impartial)

27:34.840 --> 27:35.679
My lady,

27:35.679 --> 27:36.639
dinner is ready.

27:38.800 --> 27:39.360
Coming!

27:48.399 --> 27:49.560
Come back and eat.

27:49.560 --> 27:50.760
I made your favorite dishes.

28:22.439 --> 28:24.360
Look at this lousy place you chose.

28:24.360 --> 28:25.840
Such a long way to buy medicine.

28:25.840 --> 28:27.199
It's so inconvenient.

28:27.239 --> 28:28.560
The capital is so much better.

28:28.560 --> 28:30.679
Why did you come
to such a remote, desolate place?

28:30.679 --> 28:32.239
Here, drink the medicine.

28:37.280 --> 28:38.679
The scenery here is beautiful.

28:38.919 --> 28:39.679
Isn't it nice?

28:40.360 --> 28:42.800
What's the use of beautiful scenery?
You can't even see it.

28:47.999 --> 28:48.959
Just teasing you.

28:52.399 --> 28:53.199
Here,

28:53.360 --> 28:54.239
drink the medicine.

29:05.919 --> 29:07.919
The physician said
your eyes will recover.

29:11.320 --> 29:14.080
By then, you can
watch the stars with me.

29:16.760 --> 29:18.159
Beautiful starry sky tonight?

29:22.080 --> 29:22.880
Yes.

29:33.880 --> 29:34.719
Han Mingxi?

29:35.360 --> 29:36.399
It really is you.

29:36.520 --> 29:37.439
Where have you gone?

29:37.600 --> 29:38.919
The boss has been worried.

29:39.880 --> 29:41.159
Come on. Come back with me.

29:41.560 --> 29:42.919
Let's go. Come on.

29:43.999 --> 29:45.439
What's wrong with you last time?

29:45.439 --> 29:47.639
You just left without a word.

29:47.639 --> 29:49.239
We're all worried about you.

29:49.479 --> 29:51.199
Don't forget, you still owe me a drink.

29:52.560 --> 29:54.800
Some exhaust their
entire life's strength,

29:55.159 --> 29:57.600
dashing left and right
in the maze of fate,

29:58.719 --> 30:00.120
yet still never reaching

30:00.439 --> 30:01.999
(Vast as the Earth)
that so-called fulfillment.

30:17.800 --> 30:18.560
Your Majesty.

30:34.320 --> 30:35.120
Yanqi.

30:38.679 --> 30:39.479
You're here.

30:48.159 --> 30:48.959
Mother.

30:56.439 --> 30:57.280
Yanqi.

30:59.639 --> 31:01.199
Throughout my life,

31:01.999 --> 31:03.600
I have been decisive and ruthless,

31:04.679 --> 31:06.040
and I have never regretted it.

31:10.239 --> 31:11.080
But,

31:12.520 --> 31:14.520
lying here now,

31:16.800 --> 31:18.280
once I close my eyes,

31:19.959 --> 31:21.520
I can always see

31:23.040 --> 31:23.919
those

31:25.439 --> 31:27.239
who had to leave their homes

31:28.399 --> 31:30.120
because of the Longqu official road,

31:31.280 --> 31:32.959
those who could not escape

31:34.040 --> 31:36.439
the fire of the Eastern Palace,

31:37.439 --> 31:38.880
and those wronged,

31:41.120 --> 31:42.120
unyielding soldiers

31:44.040 --> 31:46.159
of the Heiyun Cavalry.

31:51.560 --> 31:52.439
To

31:53.560 --> 31:55.439
clear the obstacles

31:56.399 --> 31:57.840
and stabilize the nation for you,

31:59.959 --> 32:01.719
I've caused

32:02.360 --> 32:03.760
indelible

32:04.679 --> 32:06.040
blood and sins.

32:17.840 --> 32:19.320
You are the emperor.

32:21.679 --> 32:23.239
You must be just.

32:25.600 --> 32:27.159
You should

32:28.520 --> 32:30.520
judge fairly.

32:35.399 --> 32:36.719
You must not

32:37.600 --> 32:39.360
show mercy

32:41.360 --> 32:43.239
just because I am your mother.

32:48.439 --> 32:49.239
Mother.

32:59.760 --> 33:00.600
You don't need

33:01.239 --> 33:02.040
to do as I did.

33:04.919 --> 33:05.880
Nor do you need

33:07.120 --> 33:08.520
to bear

33:09.159 --> 33:10.080
my sins.

33:19.159 --> 33:20.600
You must be fair

33:21.999 --> 33:23.120
and open.

33:23.479 --> 33:24.280
Stay

33:25.520 --> 33:26.600
safe.

33:32.280 --> 33:33.080
Yan...

33:39.312 --> 33:40.159
Mother.

33:43.639 --> 33:44.439
Your Majesty.

33:45.280 --> 33:46.080
Mother!

33:46.439 --> 33:47.239
Imperial physician.

33:47.399 --> 33:48.199
Imperial physician.

33:51.472 --> 33:55.600
The ancients who wished to manifest
their bright virtue to the world.

33:55.600 --> 33:57.919
First, governed their states.

33:57.919 --> 34:00.120
Those who wished to govern their states.

34:00.120 --> 34:02.520
First, regulated their families.

34:02.520 --> 34:04.560
Those who wished
to regulate their families.

34:04.719 --> 34:06.439
First, cultivated themselves.

34:07.159 --> 34:09.200
Those who wished
to cultivate themselves.

34:09.399 --> 34:11.160
First, rectified their minds.

34:11.800 --> 34:13.760
Those who wished
to rectify their minds.

34:13.760 --> 34:15.599
First, made their intentions sincere.

34:15.760 --> 34:17.760
Those who wished to make
their intentions sincere.

34:17.760 --> 34:19.680
(Lishan Academy)
First, extended their knowledge.

34:19.680 --> 34:22.240
The extension of knowledge lies
in the investigation of things.

34:28.999 --> 34:29.999
(The night may be long,)

34:30.880 --> 34:32.304
(yet it can never outlast the lamp)

34:32.304 --> 34:33.800
(that never dims in human hearts.)

34:35.160 --> 34:37.079
(We all struggle to survive
amidst the changes,)

34:37.680 --> 34:39.680
(wander in the narrow corner of fate,)

34:40.519 --> 34:42.559
(and take root like a plant in a storm.)

34:44.280 --> 34:45.439
(Until one day,)

34:46.479 --> 34:47.800
(we break through,)

34:48.959 --> 34:50.479
(and welcome a new life.)

34:58.999 --> 35:00.559
(The emperor has no private favors,)

35:01.039 --> 35:02.360
(nor any household affairs.)

35:03.280 --> 35:04.479
(The nation weighs)

35:04.999 --> 35:06.320
(heavier than any mountain.)

35:08.039 --> 35:09.439
(Granted the Mandate of Heaven,)

35:09.599 --> 35:10.880
(I rule over all lands.)

35:11.360 --> 35:13.360
I should have governed the world
with filial piety.

35:14.079 --> 35:14.599
However,

35:14.599 --> 35:15.559
Empress Dowager Guo,

35:15.999 --> 35:18.399
after the late emperor's passing,

35:18.680 --> 35:19.999
acted recklessly by her power,

35:20.360 --> 35:21.760
committing grave sins.

35:22.320 --> 35:23.800
Though she has now passed away,

35:24.119 --> 35:25.360
her crimes cannot be concealed.

35:26.119 --> 35:28.144
I have to issue an edict on her behalf,

35:28.479 --> 35:29.880
proclaiming to the world,

35:30.160 --> 35:31.360
to make her crimes clear.

35:32.119 --> 35:32.760
The first crime,

35:33.079 --> 35:34.599
setting fire to the Eastern Palace,

35:34.599 --> 35:35.919
launching a political purge,

35:36.280 --> 35:37.439
implicating the innocent,

35:38.160 --> 35:39.840
causing panic throughout the court,

35:40.079 --> 35:41.200
and disunity among people.

35:41.800 --> 35:42.680
The second crime,

35:43.039 --> 35:44.519
destroying the late emperor's edict,

35:44.800 --> 35:46.240
forging orders, usurping power,

35:46.399 --> 35:47.640
framing innocent officials,

35:47.999 --> 35:50.599
causing the Heiyun Cavalry
to suffer eight years of injustice.

35:51.160 --> 35:51.999
The third crime,

35:52.399 --> 35:54.224
attempting to usurp
the Fengshan ceremony,

35:54.288 --> 35:55.519
coveting the imperial throne,

35:55.840 --> 35:57.479
making the siege to Lishan Academy,

35:57.880 --> 36:00.039
(causing dozens
to die from the epidemic.)

36:00.479 --> 36:02.039
(Trampling on the cultural heritage)

36:02.039 --> 36:03.200
(is a crime detested by all.)

36:03.959 --> 36:05.360
(The deeds of Ms. Guo)

36:05.360 --> 36:07.959
(betrayed the ancestors
and harmed the people.)

36:08.439 --> 36:10.672
(Even heaven and earth
cannot forgive her.)

36:11.216 --> 36:12.080
(Starting today,)

36:12.080 --> 36:13.840
(all of Ms. Guo's titles
shall be abolished,)

36:13.904 --> 36:15.360
(her posthumous offerings revoked,)

36:15.360 --> 36:16.880
(and her posthumous names stripped.)

36:17.079 --> 36:18.959
(The court historians
shall record her evils.)

36:18.959 --> 36:20.560
(She'll be buried as a commoner)

36:20.560 --> 36:21.648
outside the imperial tombs.

36:22.079 --> 36:25.119
Dowager Consort Qin secretly
hidden the late emperor's edict

36:25.360 --> 36:27.999
and colluded with Marquis Muyang
to disrupt the court.

36:28.599 --> 36:29.559
Her sentence as follow.

36:29.559 --> 36:30.959
Her clan registry shall be revoked.

36:30.959 --> 36:32.399
She shall be demoted to a commoner,

36:32.399 --> 36:34.079
and imprisoned for life in Lingnan.

36:34.360 --> 36:35.440
The edict is as above.

36:35.919 --> 36:37.240
Execute upon receipt.

36:38.840 --> 36:42.032
- We obey the edict.
- We obey the edict.

36:43.919 --> 36:44.959
(The nation,)

36:45.559 --> 36:46.559
(including the people,)

36:47.240 --> 36:49.200
(is never an empire
owned by one person.)

36:50.119 --> 36:50.919
(To blame oneself)

36:51.559 --> 36:52.439
(and one's kin)

36:53.039 --> 36:54.160
(is all for the sake)

36:54.720 --> 36:56.528
(of being blameless before the world.)

36:56.528 --> 36:57.760
(Notice)

36:57.760 --> 36:59.039
Heavens finally upholds justice.

36:59.039 --> 37:00.320
Lishan Academy is reopened!

37:00.959 --> 37:01.760
Wonderful!

37:02.320 --> 37:04.720
(Lishan Academy)

37:04.840 --> 37:05.599
Look,

37:05.599 --> 37:06.559
what is this?

37:07.360 --> 37:08.959
It's great that Lishan Academy reopens.

37:10.599 --> 37:11.840
I read in a book yesterday

37:12.200 --> 37:13.439
when the supreme Dao prevails,

37:13.680 --> 37:14.800
the world is shared by all.

37:15.888 --> 37:16.840
(Lishan Academy)

37:16.840 --> 37:18.119
- Watch your step.
- Hurry.

37:18.119 --> 37:18.959
Wait for me.

37:18.959 --> 37:19.800
- Be careful.
- Careful.

37:19.800 --> 37:20.840
I can't keep up.

37:20.840 --> 37:21.680
Wait for me.

37:23.840 --> 37:25.519
Be careful.

37:29.520 --> 37:30.510
Wait for me.

37:33.760 --> 37:34.599
- Headmaster.
- Headmaster.

37:35.079 --> 37:36.360
You go ahead first.

37:36.360 --> 37:36.999
Go ahead.

37:36.999 --> 37:37.919
There are people there.

37:37.919 --> 37:38.680
Over there.

37:40.432 --> 37:41.200
Your Highness.

37:41.200 --> 37:41.840
Your Highness.

37:42.320 --> 37:43.919
I thought you arrive at the Si hour.

37:43.919 --> 37:45.240
Why are you here so early?

37:45.240 --> 37:46.599
Li couldn't wait at home.

37:46.599 --> 37:48.240
She wished to ride here overnight.

37:49.360 --> 37:50.599
Here, this way please.

37:51.680 --> 37:52.479
Don't run.

37:54.919 --> 37:56.160
It looks completely new.

37:56.640 --> 37:58.079
Headmaster Wei, you're so capable.

37:58.240 --> 37:59.760
Don't make fun of me.

37:59.999 --> 38:02.039
His Majesty wants
to reopen Lishan Academy.

38:02.039 --> 38:03.880
I received the imperial edict
just weeks ago.

38:03.880 --> 38:05.320
I've really been a bit rushed.

38:06.079 --> 38:08.280
Some windows haven't been repaired yet.

38:08.880 --> 38:10.200
It looks great in every way.

38:10.720 --> 38:12.240
Why demand perfection?

38:16.079 --> 38:17.559
Many scholars have come today.

38:17.720 --> 38:18.519
Yes.

38:18.840 --> 38:19.640
This time,

38:20.119 --> 38:22.840
we've admitted a total of 341 scholars.

38:22.840 --> 38:24.439
That far exceeds my expectations.

38:24.959 --> 38:26.959
We've also recruited
twenty more masters.

38:27.559 --> 38:28.880
Most of these masters

38:28.880 --> 38:30.999
are former scholars
who studied at Lishan Mountain.

38:31.360 --> 38:33.680
Now they're all clamoring
to come back as masters.

38:33.720 --> 38:34.519
By the way,

38:34.800 --> 38:36.160
Yunsong is back too.

38:36.559 --> 38:37.760
He insisted on staying,

38:38.240 --> 38:39.920
to be a calligraphy
and painting teacher.

38:41.919 --> 38:42.720
Excellent.

38:43.599 --> 38:44.959
For scholars from humble origins

38:44.959 --> 38:46.599
who come to study with sincerity,

38:47.200 --> 38:48.479
we'll provide them

38:49.519 --> 38:51.440
with full tuition in Li's name.

38:54.079 --> 38:55.200
Your Highness, this gesture

38:55.720 --> 38:58.280
can be considered a pioneering move
for Lishan Academy.

39:02.599 --> 39:03.519
Your Highness.

39:04.880 --> 39:05.800
Master Huo.

39:06.240 --> 39:07.280
Why are you here?

39:09.039 --> 39:10.320
Living idly in the mountains

39:10.360 --> 39:11.240
would waste

39:11.720 --> 39:13.039
what I've learned in my lifetime.

39:13.599 --> 39:15.999
Now, thanks to Headmaster Wei,

39:16.519 --> 39:17.919
I've been allowed

39:17.919 --> 39:19.640
to contribute my modest efforts

39:19.640 --> 39:21.519
and share some humble insights here.

39:22.720 --> 39:24.720
Look, that's exactly what the book says.

39:24.720 --> 39:26.079
Look, look.

39:26.079 --> 39:27.472
This book is long outdated.

39:27.792 --> 39:28.559
My lady,

39:28.559 --> 39:30.039
you're finally back.

39:30.119 --> 39:30.999
Do you miss me?

39:30.999 --> 39:32.599
- Li is here.
- Li is here.

39:32.599 --> 39:33.320
I do.

39:33.320 --> 39:34.399
I miss you too.

39:37.599 --> 39:38.399
My lady.

39:38.519 --> 39:39.959
You look so beautiful now.

39:41.200 --> 39:41.720
Li.

39:42.320 --> 39:44.039
I heard you've mastered swordsmanship.

39:44.200 --> 39:44.999
Impressive!

39:45.720 --> 39:47.160
Studying the scriptures and manuals,

39:47.160 --> 39:48.720
you've fully grasped my teachings.

39:49.079 --> 39:50.079
I always said

39:50.079 --> 39:51.919
you're a natural for martial arts.

39:51.919 --> 39:52.840
My good disciple!

39:56.200 --> 39:57.119
Brilliant!

39:57.119 --> 39:58.959
This combination of aconite and coptis,

39:58.959 --> 40:00.720
is used so well and brilliantly.

40:00.720 --> 40:02.320
I've practiced medicine for decades,

40:02.360 --> 40:03.399
yet I never thought of

40:03.399 --> 40:04.360
such risky tactics,

40:04.360 --> 40:06.280
using heat against heat
and cold against cold.

40:07.399 --> 40:08.119
What a combination

40:08.119 --> 40:10.680
of cold and heat using yin and yang!

40:10.880 --> 40:11.680
Li.

40:12.919 --> 40:13.720
Li.

40:13.840 --> 40:14.800
Good.

40:15.160 --> 40:15.959
Li.

40:15.959 --> 40:17.119
Well done.

40:17.160 --> 40:17.959
Li.

40:18.119 --> 40:18.919
Excellent.

40:19.320 --> 40:20.200
I always said,

40:20.200 --> 40:21.360
Li is remarkable.

40:21.360 --> 40:23.559
She's truly one of us from Lishan.

40:25.559 --> 40:26.559
Li.

40:26.559 --> 40:27.999
Let's talk over there.

40:28.399 --> 40:29.880
Thanks for your hard work.

40:32.816 --> 40:36.156
♪You don't need to chart a map♪

40:36.156 --> 40:39.368
♪Of every bend where love winds on♪

40:39.568 --> 40:43.037
♪Nor travel far to guide its course♪

40:43.056 --> 40:48.429
♪To warm your heart♪

40:53.200 --> 40:54.880
This journey you've taken

40:55.800 --> 40:57.079
must be exhausting.

41:04.680 --> 41:05.479
But you

41:06.240 --> 41:07.999
can't stop yet.

41:09.720 --> 41:11.959
Don't be trapped by the past.

41:14.320 --> 41:15.240
Your path

41:15.999 --> 41:17.399
lies ahead,

41:18.039 --> 41:19.559
not behind you.

41:20.880 --> 41:22.280
Understood?

41:23.999 --> 41:25.160
I understand.

41:28.959 --> 41:29.760
Li.

41:30.720 --> 41:31.519
Li.

41:34.599 --> 41:35.399
Alright.

41:36.800 --> 41:38.320
Now that you understand,

41:40.200 --> 41:41.519
go then.

41:41.519 --> 41:44.432
♪You sent out the light♪

41:45.341 --> 41:47.504
♪From far, far away♪

41:47.504 --> 41:51.899
♪Leaves are like broad, gentle hands♪

41:52.321 --> 41:54.960
♪Wiping away your tears♪

41:55.088 --> 41:58.527
♪With broadest shoulders♪

41:59.053 --> 42:02.448
♪To soar in skies above♪

42:08.959 --> 42:09.760
Now,

42:10.399 --> 42:11.439
all scholars,

42:12.320 --> 42:13.200
you may enter.

42:14.280 --> 42:15.320
- Yes.
- Yes.

42:28.560 --> 42:33.302
♪Time is flowing moonlight♪

42:33.392 --> 42:36.304
♪Treasuring memories♪

42:36.432 --> 42:39.658
♪You sent out the light♪

42:40.224 --> 42:43.248
♪From far, far away♪

42:43.248 --> 42:47.248
♪You don't need to chase♪

42:47.248 --> 42:50.128
♪No need to chase♪

42:50.928 --> 43:03.376
(Promoting Education
and Fostering Talent)

43:04.657 --> 43:08.880
(The end)

43:15.736 --> 43:22.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.912 --> 43:32.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:34.264 --> 43:37.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.720 --> 43:43.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:44.056 --> 43:47.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.544 --> 43:54.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:55.160 --> 43:59.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:59.096 --> 44:04.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:05.304 --> 44:13.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.808 --> 44:20.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:20.312 --> 44:25.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.880 --> 44:29.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:30.232 --> 44:35.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:36.056 --> 44:39.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.800 --> 44:45.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:46.232 --> 44:54.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.608 --> 45:00.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:01.112 --> 45:07.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:07.016 --> 45:11.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.352 --> 45:16.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:17.304 --> 45:21.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.816 --> 45:27.256
♪Unbound by form♪
